{"tid":1771054,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［招場地］觀塘年宵見","createTime":"2019-12-05T14:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T02:56:25.000Z","uid":146909,"like":105,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3c1ef6604b77f0f36eba7f4965a87c85706320","tid":1771054,"uid":146909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係飯堂老闆。<br />\n<br />\n行年宵，我諗都算係香港人嘅集體回憶之一。<br />\n<br />\n今日因為呢個壞咗嘅政府而令我哋冇得去行年宵，我覺得好難過。<br />\n<br />\n不過既然有流水式集會，咁又會唔會有流水式行年宵呢？<br />\n<br />\n而有鑒於和你宵原來係一個騙局，我同班小朋友決定喺工廠大廈搞一個大型嘅連鎖市集，取代年宵。工廠尋寶模式，串連開源道附近唔同場地，輔以map介紹地方。<br />\n<br />\n我哋而家物色緊一啲可以提供空間比人哋擺檔嘅場地，大小不苟，只要至少擺到一、兩個攤檔就可以。<br />\n<br />\n日期:23-24/1（暫定）<br />\n地點：觀塘工業區<br />\n我地財政絕對公開<br />\n唔需要場租，入場費<br />\n中央財政，確保檔主收入透明，避免人血饅頭。<br />\n<br />\n但由於時間有限，需要好多人幫手物色場地，如果有相關資源，請聯絡我。<br />\nTg：@irwin0616<br />\nTel：6373 7922<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔知我係邊個，可以參考呢個post：<br />\n飯堂老闆有話兒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n附上相關計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWLQ4qC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWLQ4qC.jpg&h=a8b8108f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CoSoEYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoSoEYY.jpg&h=252750bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cBMCLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cBMCLE.jpg&h=dce29e99&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyA2a5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyA2a5F.jpg&h=95e0c725&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tWHVxk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tWHVxk.jpg&h=aedca3a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17c43ee5cd823a4956611771a2da013b740e300e","tid":1771054,"uid":146909,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:34:54.000Z","msg":